name: Marble Blast Gold Reverse
description:
All Marble Blast Gold levels with the start pad and end pad switched in position. There are some that I thought wouldn't be possible so I added powerups. Feel free to prove me wrong.
The "impossible" ones are: Air Movement, Block Party, Darwin's Dilemma, Dive!, Free Fall, Go for the Green, Grand Finale, Gravity Helix, Great Divide, Great Divide Revisited, Gyrocopter, Hoops, Hop Skip and a Jump, Icarus, Leap of Faith, Learn the Super Speed, Pinball Wizard, Shock Absorber, Shock Drop, Ski Slopes, Super Bounce, Survival of the Fittest and Tri Twist for a total of 23.
Since uploading the levels here, Hoops Reverse and Survival of the Fittest Reverse have been proven to be possible without the extra powerups.
